window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After accidentally shifting into a wolf - and getting stuck - Tehya, herself a vampire, has spent the last 12 years as the pet of Lobo, another vampire who has the unique gift of communicating with wolves.</p> <p>When Lobo found Tehya starving and nearly frozen to death, he took her in and nursed her back to health, all the while completely unaware that she was really a fellow vampire. But there was always something special about her, and he finds out exactly how special after she's injured and returned to her true form.</p> <p>Desire collides with danger as he soon finds that he must protect not only Tehya but also himself.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
